title: (GS) Curry Brand Sesame Street x Curry Flow 9 'Street Pack - Cookie Monster'  3024249-404
description: Introducing the cool new Under Armour Sesame Street x Curry Flow 9 GS 'Street Pack Cookie Monster' sneaker. This attractive and trusty shoe is designed with your comfort and performance in mind. This durable sneaker is made entirely rubber-free, making them contain more grip, be lighter weight and provide optimum cushioning for all activities. The woven TPU yarns in shades of blue wind will add stunning detail, while the black tongue and heel counter explore a sleek contrast. A added bonus to this slick style is the pull tab which comes with a fuzzy blue piece inspired by the beloved Cookie Monster’s furry coat – complete with his eyes featured on the ankle collar! The performance of this shoe is achieved through the lightweight Flow midsole/outsole construction as well as Steph Curry's logo on the lateral side. Enjoy you adventures in style and maximum performance every time in your Under Armour Sesame Street x Curry Flow 9 GS 'Street Pack Cookie Monster' sneaker.
